ating\" style=\"left: 80%; animation-delay: 2s;\">✨</div>\r\n<div class=\"floating\" style=\"left: 90%; animation-delay: 3.5s;\">💖</div>\r\n<div class=\"thank-you-card\">\r\n<div class=\"header\">\r\n<div class=\"big-check\">\r\n<div class=\"check\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h1>WOW! Thank You!</h1>\r\n<div class=\"subtitle\">Your donation was received with joy 🎉</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n<p class=\"message\">You just made someone’s day brighter!\r\nBecause of your generosity, we’re one step closer to changing lives.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rainbow-text\">You’re INCREDIBLE! 🌈</div>\r\n<div class=\"extra\">\r\n\r\nEvery dollar creates hope. Thank you for being our hero today ❤️\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<a class=\"btn-home\" href=\"/\">← Back to Home</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- Simple confetti script (pure CSS, no library needed) -->\r\n<script>\r\n    setInterval(() => {\r\n      const emoji = [\'❤️\',\'✨\',\'💖\',\'⭐\',\'🌟\',\'🎉\',\'💝\',\'🥳\'];\r\n      const f = document.createElement(\'div\');\r\n      f.className = \'floating\';\r\n      f.style.left = Math.random() * 100 + \'%\';\r\n      f.style.animationDuration = (Math.random() * 5 + 5) + \'s\';\r\n      f.innerText = emoji[Math.floor(Math.random() * emoji.length)];\r\n      document.body.appendChild(f);\r\n      setTimeout(() => f.remove(), 10000);\r\n    }, 600);\r\n  </script>', 'Thank You For The Donation', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '350-revision-v1', '', '', '2025-11-28 04:36:46', '2025-11-28 04:36:46', '', 350, 'http://localhost/ukroa/?p=354', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
