der-target design-element-background-layer has-rich-content user-selectable-element clickable-element has-rich-content rich-content-element\" data-element-id=\"id1489678315183\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"element-border-box element-border-target element-padding-box design-element-border-box has-rich-content user-selectable-element clickable-element has-rich-content rich-content-element\" data-element-id=\"id1489678315183\">\r\n<div class=\"element-content-box design-element-content-box has-rich-content user-selectable-element clickable-element has-rich-content rich-content-element\" data-element-id=\"id1489678315183\">\r\n<div class=\"content-container content-container-type element-size-box element-size-target has-rich-content user-selectable-element clickable-element has-rich-content rich-content-element\" data-element-id=\"id1489678315183\">\r\n<div class=\"rich-content common-rich-content-style element-content has-content\">\r\n\r\nEvent: UKROA Annual General Meeting 2020\r\nDate of event: Sunday June 14 th , 2020\r\nTime of event: 5:00 pm – 11:00 pm EST\r\nLocation of event: VIA Zoom\r\nNumber of Persons in attendance: Estimated 100\r\n\r\nOn June 14 th 2020, UKROA hosted its annual General Meeting. Each year, executive board members from all 5 UKROA chapters convene to\r\nsummarize the organization’s events and finances of the year and collaborate with each other. In addition, high school and university graduates were recognized for their achievements. Performances from members in the community were displayed as well. The unfortunate and unforeseen pandemic posed a challenge to this annual event this year. However, UKROA responded productively and proactively and successfully conducted the entire event online via Zoom. This year’s general meeting was an overall success despite the covid-19 pandemic situation.\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</article></div>', 'Annual General Meeting 2020', '', 'inhe